{"tid":2138691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮貿易顧問Navarro : 微軟若要買TikTok 宜從中國撤資","createTime":"2020-08-03T18:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T19:41:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6fa1ca0ca862839e91eaf029b516b1924c709b8","tid":2138691,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/08/03 23:54<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓3日綜合外電報導）傳聞美國總統川普同意給TikTok母公司北京字節跳動科技45天時間，協商出售TikTok給美國微軟公司事宜。白宮貿易顧問納瓦洛今天暗示，微軟若想買下TikTok，可能該由中國撤資。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛（Peter Navarro）接受有線電視新聞網（CNN）訪問時說：「問題在於微軟（Microsoft Corp）是否會受到危害？也許微軟可以放棄在中國的投資。」<br />\n<br />\n3位了解內情人士透露，美國總統川普已同意給字節跳動科技45天時間，協商把短影音平台TikTok賣給微軟的事宜。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛稍早接受福斯新聞頻道（Fox News Channel）訪問時表示，TikTok的任何潛在買家若在中國有業務都可能會有問題。<br />\n<br />\n他舉微軟的Bing搜尋引擎和Skype通訊平台為例說，二者「實際上都使得中國得以實施審查、偵測和監控」。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦參議院民主黨領袖舒默（Chuck Schumer）則表示：「務必要找出安全方法讓TikTok能持續運作。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202008030339.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202008030339.aspx&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0OxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e76f32cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202008030339.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"99a128d6fddfce8e1d31c83814ca40d08416f60d","tid":2138691,"uid":156652,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWc3mJp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWc3mJp.gif&h=f05500a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d467f6cec14a8de5d7143c0f188a1dc2166cab67","tid":2138691,"uid":270889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T18:24:19.000Z","msg":"sai 9 hey la<br />\n學印度一野ban咗佢就唔洗煩"},{"pid":"cb4138b4eb8df4566b581211fc6784e03904c230","tid":2138691,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T18:40:34.000Z","msg":"Ban <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif